    <intervention_name>Remote Ischemic Preconditioning</intervention_name>
    <description>RIPC will be induced during anesthesia by four 5-min cycles of upper limb ischemia and 5-min reperfusion using a blood-pressure cuff inflated to a pressure 15 mm Hg greater than the systolic arterial pressure measured via the arterial line.</description>
